				<img src={avatar} />
			</div> -->
		</div>
		<p class="instructions text-black dark:text-white bg-stone-200 dark:bg-stone-700">
			I'm an aspiring <strong>front-end web developer</strong> with a flair for crafting captivating and user-friendly websites. My journey began with personal projects and freelance work, evolving into a passionate commitment to coding over the past years. I've immersed myself in the dynamic world of web development, constantly refining my skills and staying current with the latest technologies.
