			I recently completed the web developer program at <strong>IThub College</strong>, equipping me with a solid foundation in programming languages and best practices. Based in <strong>Norfolk, UK</strong>, I'm excited about joining a forward-thinking team to contribute my technical expertise and creative problem-solving skills. My dedication, coupled with my education, makes me confident in thriving as a web developer.
